{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_1780196078500_jegotijfoo","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"claude-4.7-opus","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" Looking at this 28-year-old with an acute upper respiratory infection—the clinical picture is pretty straightforward for a viral etiology. He's got a three-day cough with low-grade fever and clear sputum, and all the inflammatory markers are reassuring: normal WBC, normal CRP, and normal procalcitonin all point toward a viral process rather than bacterial infection. His vitals and oxygen saturation are stable, which is good.\n\nThe physical exam shows mild throat congestion without exudate, and he has no relevant medical history or medications that would complicate management. Given the clinical guidelines for viral URIs, I'm avoiding antibiotics entirely since there's no bacterial indication. Instead, I'm focusing on symptomatic relief with acetaminophen for fever if it exceeds 38.5°C and ambroxol to help with the white sputum and cough. The rest of the management is supportive—adequate rest, hydration, and monitoring for any changes. I'm steering clear of combination cold medications and sticking to single agents, which is cleaner and safer.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":32499,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3c307a58-a104-428d-90b2-c7396bd28596","uuid":"dff84fee-d505-4d5a-ae1f-660c74e2940d"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_1780196078500_jegotijfoo","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"claude-4.7-opus","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Patient is a healthy 28yo male with classic viral URI (J06.9) — normal WBC/CRP/PCT, mild throat congestion only, low-grade fever, white sputum. No antibiotic indication. Symptomatic treatment is appropriate."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":32499,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3c307a58-a104-428d-90b2-c7396bd28596","uuid":"c0048585-8e87-4819-b6a5-7c65a9ff3acc"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_1780196078500_jegotijfoo","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"claude-4.7-opus","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"tooluse_PNl4OVf0VRJOXal3i5045v","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"curl -s -X POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/prescriptions \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"patient_id\": \"P0000123\",\n    \"encounter_id\": \"ENC-20260530-0042\",\n    \"diagnosis\": [\n      {\"icd10\": \"J06.9\", \"name\": \"急性上呼吸道感染\", \"is_primary\": true}\n    ],\n    \"prescription_items\": [\n      {\n        \"generic_name\": \"对乙酰氨基酚\",\n        \"specification\": \"0.5g/片\",\n        \"dose\": 0.5,\n        \"dose_unit\": \"g\",\n        \"frequency\": \"prn\",\n        \"route\": \"PO\",\n        \"duration_days\": 0,\n        \"total_quantity\": \"6片\",\n        \"instructions\": \"体温>38.5℃或明显头痛/肌痛时服用，两次间隔≥6小时，24小时内不超过4次（≤2g/日）\",\n        \"indication\": \"发热/头身痛对症\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"generic_name\": \"氨溴索\",\n        \"specification\": \"30mg/片\",\n        \"dose\": 30,\n        \"dose_unit\": \"mg\",\n        \"frequency\": \"tid\",\n        \"route\": \"PO\",\n        \"duration_days\": 5,\n        \"total_quantity\": \"15片\",\n        \"instructions\": \"饭后口服，多饮水有助于稀释痰液\",\n        \"indication\": \"咳嗽伴白痰，黏痰祛痰治疗\"\n      }\n    ],\n    \"non_drug_advice\": [\n      \"充分休息，避免劳累，注意保暖\",\n      \"多饮温水（每日 1.5-2L），清淡饮食\",\n      \"房间通风，可使用加湿器缓解气道刺激\",\n      \"可用淡盐水漱口或温盐水含漱缓解咽部不适\",\n      \"戴口罩，咳嗽/打喷嚏时遮挡，注意手卫生，避免传染家人\",\n      \"避免吸烟、饮酒及辛辣刺激性食物\",\n      \"如自觉症状可控，可暂不服用退热药（37.8℃属低热，无需强行退热）\"\n    ],\n    \"clinical_reasoning\": \"患者男性 28 岁，既往体健，无过敏史，无合并症及合并用药，肝肾功能正常。主诉咳嗽发热 3 天，受凉起病，白色少量痰，最高体温 37.8℃，咽部轻度充血无脓苔，肺部听诊清晰。血常规 WBC 7.8、N% 62 均正常，CRP 4.1（<10）、PCT 0.05（<0.5）均不支持细菌感染——综合临床表现+实验室指标，诊断急性病毒性上呼吸道感染（J06.9）明确。\\n\\n(1) 治疗策略：病毒性 URI 系自限性疾病，以对症支持治疗为主，不开具抗生素及抗病毒药物。\\n(2) 选药依据：① 对乙酰氨基酚作为退热/镇痛首选，安全性高，NRDL 甲类；prn 给药，仅在 T>38.5℃或头身痛明显时服用，避免常规使用掩盖病情；单次 0.5g、间隔 ≥6h、≤2g/日，远低于 4g/日的最大剂量上限，肝功正常无累积风险。② 氨溴索用于黏液溶解促进白痰排出，常规剂量 30mg tid×5 天；NRDL 乙类无限制条件。\\n(3) 个体化匹配：青年男性，体重 68kg，肝肾功能正常，无过敏史及合并用药——所选药物均为常规剂量，无需调整；无相互作用顾虑。\\n(4) 监测/复诊：嘱患者观察症状演变，5-7 天内多数自限缓解；若出现高热持续>3 天、脓黄痰、胸痛气促、咯血、嗜睡精神差等危险征兆需立即复诊，警惕继发细菌感染或下呼吸道感染。\",\n    \"explicit_avoidance\": [\n      {\"drug_or_class\": \"抗生素（如阿莫西林、头孢类、阿奇霉素等）\", \"reason\": \"WBC/N%/CRP/PCT 全部正常，咽部无脓苔，肺部清音，临床综合判断为病毒性 URI，无细菌感染证据；无指征预防性使用抗生素，避免耐药性及不良反应风险。\"},\n      {\"drug_or_class\": \"奥司他韦等神经氨酸酶抑制剂\", \"reason\": \"无流感流行季高暴露史、无典型流感样症状（高热寒战+全身肌痛），症状轻微，发病已 3 天进入抗病毒治疗最佳窗口外，无 NAI 使用指征。\"},\n      {\"drug_or_class\": \"复方感冒制剂（含伪麻黄碱/氯苯那敏等多组分）\", \"reason\": \"患者症状以咳嗽白痰为主，无明显鼻塞流涕；单组分按症给药更精准，避免多组分复方制剂的重复用药与不必要副作用（嗜睡、心悸、对乙酰氨基酚叠加超量）。\"},\n      {\"drug_or_class\": \"镇咳药（如右美沙芬、可待因）\", \"reason\": \"患者为湿性咳嗽伴白痰，痰液需排出，强行抑制咳嗽反射不利于痰液清除；以祛痰为主即可。\"},\n      {\"drug_or_class\": \"糖皮质激素（口服/全身）\", \"reason\": \"普通病毒性 URI 无激素使用指征。\"},\n      {\"drug_or_class\": \"中成药抗病毒口服液\", \"reason\": \"证据级别有限，且患者主诉自服板蓝根 3 天未见明显好转，无继续/换用指征；以休息+对症治疗为主。\"}\n    ],\n    \"follow_up\": {\n      \"next_visit_days\": 7,\n      \"red_flags\": [\n        \"发热持续>3 天不退或体温>39℃\",\n        \"出现黄绿色脓痰或血痰\",\n        \"胸痛、气促、呼吸困难、SpO2 下降\",\n        \"意识淡漠、嗜睡、剧烈头痛\",\n        \"症状加重或新发耳痛/鼻窦疼痛/扁桃体脓性分泌物\"\n      ]\n    }\n  }'","description":"Submit prescription for viral URI"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":32499,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3c307a58-a104-428d-90b2-c7396bd28596","uuid":"b704b2fa-ac8c-4691-bf6e-94bcf8c18a4f"}
